# Showcase

@callout .ok
    This page showcases a layout override using the `topnav` layout.
@end callout

The different layouts are:

- `topnav`: the one currently being used
- `sidebar`: the default one

the `topnav` layout puts folders into a dropdown menu that opens on hover. the `sidebar` menu automatically shows them on the side.

